1. *Rebeka* je bila oduševljena kada je videla poklon koji joj je stigao. (Rebecca was thrilled when she saw the gift that had arrived for her.)
2. Volim da čitam knjige o *Rebeki*, ona je neverovatno hrabra žena. (I love reading books about Rebecca, she is an incredibly brave woman.)
3. Da li si čula da će *Rebeki* biti uručena nagrada za hrabrost? (Have you heard that Rebecca will be awarded for her bravery?)
4. Upravo sam gledao film o *Rebeki*, moraš ga pogledati. (I just watched a movie about Rebecca, you have to see it.)
5. *Rebeku* sam upoznao pre nekoliko godina i od tada smo postali dobri prijatelji. (I met Rebecca a few years ago, and since then, we have become good friends.)
6. Znaš li gde je *Rebekina* kuća? (Do you know where Rebecca's house is?)
7. Molim te, donesi mi *Rebekinu* adresu. (Please, bring me Rebecca's address.)
8. Planiramo da posetimo *Rebeku* sledećeg vikenda. (We're planning to visit Rebecca next weekend.)
9. *Rebekin* uspeh inspiriše mnoge žene širom sveta. (Rebecca's success inspires many women around the world.)
10. Nadam se da će *Rebekin* novi posao biti uspešan. (I hope Rebecca's new job will be successful.)